00:35:15,994 --> 00:35:17,575
And we wanted to get some of that memory back,

566
00:35:17,615 --> 00:35:19,176
so we ended up cutting some things.

567
00:35:20,217 --> 00:35:23,439
We went through multiple pipeline iterations when working on

568
00:35:23,479 --> 00:35:24,500
the vanity system.

569
00:35:25,521 --> 00:35:28,723
